"version": "1.0.4",
"title": "6738: rescue",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6738",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Deliverance from people or forces that are overwhelming. It implies a liberator with strength and wisdom to ensure true freedom. God's physical rescue of the Israelites points to the spiritual deliverance obtained by Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>When rescue is the only answer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:10\">PSA 35:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:27\">DEU 22:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:29\">DEU 28:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:21\">1SA 12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:22\">ISA 42:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:4\">DAN 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:7\">DAN 8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:14\">HOS 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:8\">MIC 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:24\">ROM 7:24</a></p>\n<h2>God's power to rescue in times of need</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10\">ISA 41:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:13\">1CO 10:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:9-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:9–12:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:6\">HEB 13:6</a></p>\n<h2>God's people cry to him for rescue</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg10:15\">JDG 10:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:8\">1SA 7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:11\">PSA 22:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:17\">PSA 35:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:1\">PSA 43:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:13-Ps69:14\">PSA 69:13–69:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:2\">PSA 71:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:19\">PSA 107:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:1\">PSA 140:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:6\">PSA 142:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:9\">PSA 143:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:7\">PSA 144:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:11\">PRO 24:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:31\">ROM 15:31</a> <em>Paul's need for protection</em></p>\n<h2>God's physical rescue of his people</h2>\n<h3>From their enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:8\">EXO 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:14\">JDG 6:14</a>EXO <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:10\">18:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:13\">1SA 11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:17-2Sam22:20\">2SA 22:17–22:20</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:16-Ps18:19\">PSA 18:16–18:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:5\">2KI 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:14\">1CH 11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:15\">2CH 20:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:22\">2CH 32:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:27\">NEH 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:14\">EST 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:13\">JER 20:13</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:29\">2CH 20:29</a> <em>Israel's enemies recognise God's rescue of his people.</em></p>\n<h3>From trouble</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:27\">DAN 6:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:7\">GEN 45:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:19\">JOB 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:7\">PSA 32:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:14-Ps91:15\">PSA 91:14–91:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:1\">PSA 126:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:8\">PRO 11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:32\">JOL 2:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:10\">JON 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:9\">2PE 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>From oppression</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:12-Ps72:14\">PSA 72:12–72:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:3-Ps82:4\">PSA 82:3–82:4</a></p>\n<h2>God's spiritual rescue of believers</h2>\n<h3>From the guilt, penalty and power of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">LUK 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:11-Jer29:14\">JER 29:11–29:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:21\">ROM 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:10\">1TH 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></p>\n<h3>From the dominion of Satan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:13\">COL 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">MAT 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:74\">LUK 1:74</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:1\">LUK 9:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:21-Luke11:22\">LUK 11:21–11:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:16\">LUK 13:16</a></p>\n<h3>From spiritual attack</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:18\">2TI 4:18</a></p>\n<h3>From fear and the fear of death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14-Heb2:15\">HEB 2:14–2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:4\">PSA 34:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:54-1Cor15:57\">1CO 15:54–15:57</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:10\">2CO 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a></p>\n<h2>Rescuers sent by God</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:34\">ACT 7:34</a> <em>Moses</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:9\">JDG 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:15\">JDG 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg10:1\">JDG 10:1</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of people rescued</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:10\">ACT 7:10</a> <em>Joseph</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6-Jer38:13\">JER 38:6–38:13</a> <em>Jeremiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:17\">DAN 3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:28\">DAN 3:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:21-Dan6:23\">DAN 6:21–6:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:27\">DAN 6:27</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:11\">ACT 12:11</a> <em>Peter</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:27\">ACT 23:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:17\">ACT 26:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:11\">2TI 3:11</a></p>",
